name: Godzilla Energy
description:
A few weeks ago, my son - Moan, took my ipad and started drawing on it.

He is very happy when he draws while telling stories.

Moan said, "This is a godzilla that spits fire. A tank wheeled godzilla that fights against heat energies".

Very interesting! Ha ha ha

Then I made a picture made by Moan as a skin mask for drrtydobz. Enjoy this collaboration!
